attributes.Long form description: The student assembles the Rolling cart. First, the student assembles the base frame, and following screws the sidebars and attaches it to the base frame. Then assembles the low tray, and places the middle tray, the instructor tells him to place it into the low tray, so he puts it into the low tray and assembles the top tray. Next, screws the middle tray. At last, he inserts the wheels.

attributes.Transcription: We will not assemble actually from IKEA.
So you can go ahead and start.
